graph LR
    Notebooks["Notebooks<br/>(Workbench Image Factory)"]

    %% Base Image Dependencies
    Notebooks -->|base image| UBI9["UBI9 Python 3.12"]
    Notebooks -->|GPU runtime| CUDA["CUDA Toolkit 12.9.1<br/>cuDNN 9.14, NCCL 2.27"]
    Notebooks -->|AMD GPU| ROCm["ROCm 6.4"]

    %% ML Framework Dependencies
    Notebooks -->|deep learning| PyTorch["PyTorch 2.10.0<br/>torchvision 0.25"]
    Notebooks -->|deep learning| TensorFlow["TensorFlow 2.21+redhat<br/>Keras 3.14"]
    Notebooks -->|model compression| LLMCompressor["LLMCompressor 0.10.0"]

    %% IDE / Server Dependencies
    Notebooks -->|VS Code backend| CodeServer["code-server 4.106.3"]
    Notebooks -->|R IDE| RStudioServer["RStudio Server 2025.09"]
    Notebooks -->|R runtime| RLang["R 4.5.1"]
    Notebooks -->|JS runtime| NodeJS["Node.js 22.21.1"]

    %% Infrastructure Dependencies
    Notebooks -->|reverse proxy| Nginx["nginx 1.24"]
    Notebooks -->|CGI endpoints| Httpd["httpd (Apache) 2.4"]
    Notebooks -->|doc export| Pandoc["Pandoc 3.7.0.2"]

    %% Internal ODH Platform Dependencies
    NotebookCtrl["odh-notebook-controller"] -->|creates pods from| Notebooks
    RhodsOp["rhods-operator"] -->|deploys manifests| Notebooks
    KubeRBAC["kube-rbac-proxy"] -->|auth sidecar for| Notebooks
    DashboardComp["Dashboard"] -->|reads image annotations| Notebooks
    DSPipelines["Data Science Pipelines"] -->|executes in runtime images| Notebooks

    %% Integration Points (outbound from workbenches)
    Notebooks -.->|pipeline submission| KubeTraining["Kubeflow Training Operator"]
    Notebooks -.->|experiment tracking| MLflow["MLflow v3.10"]
    Notebooks -.->|object storage| S3["S3 Storage (boto3)"]
    Notebooks -.->|version control| Git["Git Repositories"]
    Notebooks -.->|cluster mgmt| K8sAPI["OpenShift API"]

    %% Build Dependencies
    Notebooks -->|hermetic builds| KonfluxCI["Konflux CI + Cachi2"]
    Notebooks -->|image registry| RegistryRH["registry.redhat.io"]

    %% Styling
    style Notebooks fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:4px,color:#fff

